{"tid":844134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局：「轉數快」首日錄逾5萬宗交易　涉資逾2億元","createTime":"2018-10-01T15:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T16:58:33.000Z","uid":113000,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f840e1b4e9cde03f88ee22581eb4ce5b457975f","tid":844134,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420795-20181001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420795-20181001.htm&d=M1VmsWtZ%2BnMMu39uF9Nqy9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0aaa0800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420795-20181001.htm&h=e0ed6af6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420795-20181001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金管局公布，快速支付系統「轉數快」在昨日開通首日運作大致暢順，共錄得超過5萬宗交易，包括轉帳及扣帳；而經「轉數快」進行的交易金額則超過2億元，當中人民幣佔160 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n金管局表示， 所有參與「轉數快」的21家銀行及10間電子錢包營運商，亦於首日順利啟動系統及開始發放客戶應用程式更新。部分營運商為確保運作暢順，會分批為客戶開啟「轉數快」功能，所有客戶應在數天內獲得應用程式更新和可使用新功能。"},{"pid":"21695965d84f53e9e6b8378e05b71d92011e8383","tid":844134,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b14ceaed0ba1af0c0dd133db510c7b77381440","tid":844134,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"有無api<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b71d1dd52032f098a4078e29fdd8982902a8014","tid":844134,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b14ceaed0ba1af0c0dd133db510c7b77381440","tid":844134,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"有無api<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"API 要有銀行牌/SVF 牌先有"},{"pid":"9330861173b